===核反应===
中微子可以与原子核发生反应，产生一种新的原子核。放射化学[[中微子探测器|中微子探测器]]就是依靠这一过程工作的。估算一个原子核发生这种反应的概率需要考虑它的能级以及自旋态。通常发生这一反应的概率会随着原子核中中子和质子的数量的增加而变大。[[薩德伯里微中子觀測站|薩德伯里微中子觀測站]]利用[[重水|重水]]探测器发现了中微子与[[氘|氘]]核的反应。<ref name=SNO2001>{{cite web |date=4 December 2001 |title=The Sudbury Neutrino Observatory – Canada's eye on the universe |url=http://cerncourier.com/cws/article/cern/28553 |work=CERN Courier |publisher=CERN |accessdate=2008-06-04 |quote=The detector consists of a 12 m diameter acrylic sphere containing 1000 tonnes of heavy water...[Solar neutrinos] are detected at SNO via the charged current process of electron neutrinos interacting with deuterons to produce two protons and an electron |archive-date=2016-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625002601/http://cerncourier.com/cws/article/cern/28553 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

与中子类似，中微子也可以诱发重核的裂变<ref>{{cite journal |arxiv=astro-ph/0308350 |bibcode=2004PhRvL..92k1101K |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.92.111101 |pmid=15089120 |title=Neutrino-Induced Fission of Neutron-Rich Nuclei |journal=Physical Review Letters |volume=92 |issue=11 |pages=111101 |year=2004 |last1=Kolbe |first1=E. |last2=Langanke |first2=K. |last3=Fuller |first3=G. M. }}</ref>。但到目前为止，这一反应仍没有在实验室中观测到。但人们预测在恒星以及超新星中会发生这种反应。这一过程会影响宇宙中同位素的丰度。<ref>{{cite journal  |arxiv=hep-ex/0312045 |bibcode=2005PhLB..616...48K |doi=10.1016/j.physletb.2005.04.074 |title=Cross sections and fragment distributions from neutrino-induced fission on r-process nuclei |journal=Physics Letters B |volume=616 |issue=1–2 |pages=48–58 |year=2005 |last1=Kelić |first1=A. |last2=Zinner |first2=N. |last3=Kolbe |first3=E. |last4=Langanke |first4=K. |last5=Schmidt |first5=K.-H. }}</ref>

