 }}</ref>一项由{{link-en|劳厄—郎之万研究所|Institut Laue-Langevin}}完成的对于电子能谱的分析<ref>{{cite journal |arxiv=1101.2663 |doi=10.1103/PhysRevC.83.054615 |bibcode=2011PhRvC..83e4615M |title=Improved predictions of reactor antineutrino spectra |journal=Physical Review C |volume=83 |issue=5 |pages=054615 |year=2011 |last1=Mueller |first1=Th. A. |last2=Lhuillier |first2=D. |last3=Fallot |first3=M. |last4=Letourneau |first4=A. |last5=Cormon |first5=S. |last6=Fechner |first6=M. |last7=Giot |first7=L. |last8=Lasserre |first8=T. |last9=Martino |first9=J. |last10=Mention |first10=G. |last11=Porta |first11=A. |last12=Yermia |first12=F. }}</ref>也表明惰性中微子可能存在。<ref>{{cite journal |arxiv=1101.2755 |doi=10.1103/PhysRevD.83.073006 |bibcode=2011PhRvD..83g3006M |title=Reactor antineutrino anomaly |journal=Physical Review D |volume=83 |issue=7 |pages=073006 |year=2011 |last1=Mention |first1=G. |last2=Fechner |first2=M. |last3=Lasserre |first3=Th. |last4=Mueller |first4=Th. A. |last5=Lhuillier |first5=D. |last6=Cribier |first6=M. |last7=Letourneau |first7=A. }}</ref>

