 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074448/http://128.32.107.10/neutrino/PhysicsWorld.pdf
 | dead-url =no
 }}</ref>{{rp|37-38}}

对于中微子质量上限最强的理论预测来源于[[物理宇宙学|物理宇宙学]]。[[大爆炸|大爆炸]]模型理论预测了[[宇宙微波背景辐射|宇宙微波背景辐射]]中，中微子和[[光子|光子]]数量之比是固定的。如果三种中微子一起计算，每个中微子的平均能量如果超过{{val|50|ul=eV}}的话，那么宇宙就会发生坍缩。<ref name="Hut1979">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/0370-2693(79)90039-X |bibcode=1979PhLB...87..144H |title=A cosmological upper limit on the mass of heavy neutrinos |journal=Physics Letters B |volume=87 |issue=1–2 |pages=144–6 |year=1979 |last1=Hut |first1=P. |last2=Olive |first2=K.A. }}</ref>如果中微子是不稳定的，那么这一限度可能并不存在。囿于标准模型，这一点很难成立。而对于[[宇宙微波背景辐射|宇宙微波背景辐射]]、[[红移巡天|红移巡天]]以及[[莱曼α森林|莱曼α森林]]等宇宙学数据的分析给出了一个更为严格约束：三种中微子质量之和不大于{{val|0.3|u=eV}}。<ref>{{cite journal |arxiv=astro-ph/0602155 |bibcode=2006JCAP...06..019G |doi=10.1088/1475-7516/2006/06/019 |title=The neutrino mass bound from WMAP 3 year data, the baryon acoustic peak, the SNLS supernovae and the Lyman-α forest |journal=Journal of Cosmology and Astroparticle Physics |volume=2006 |issue=6 |pages=019 |year=2006 |last1=Goobar |first1=Ariel |last2=Hannestad |first2=Steen |last3=Mörtsell |first3=Edvard |last4=Tu |first4=Huitzu }}</ref>

1998年，[[超级神冈探测器|超级神冈探测器]]的研究结果证实了中微子的味可以发生振荡，并进一步得出中微子质量非零。<ref>{{cite journal |arxiv=hep-ex/9805021 |bibcode=1998PhRvL..81.1158F |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.81.1158 |title=Measurements of the Solar Neutrino Flux from Super-Kamiokande's First 300 Days |journal=Physical Review Letters |volume=81 |issue=6 |pages=1158 |year=1998 |last1=Fukuda |first1=Y. |last2=Hayakawa |first2=T. |last3=Ichihara |first3=E. |last4=Inoue |first4=K. |last5=Ishihara |first5=K. |last6=Ishino |first6=H. |last7=Itow |first7=Y. |last8=Kajita |first8=T. |last9=Kameda |first9=J. |last10=Kasuga |first10=S. |last11=Kobayashi |first11=K. |last12=Kobayashi |first12=Y. |last13=Koshio |first13=Y. |last14=Martens |first14=K. |last15=Miura |first15=M. |last16=Nakahata |first16=M. |last17=Nakayama |first17=S. |last18=Okada |first18=A. |last19=Oketa |first19=M. |last20=Okumura |first20=K. |last21=Ota |first21=M. |last22=Sakurai |first22=N. |last23=Shiozawa |first23=M. |last24=Suzuki |first24=Y. |last25=Takeuchi |first25=Y. |last26=Totsuka |first26=Y. |last27=Yamada |first27=S. |last28=Earl |first28=M. |last29=Habig |first29=A. |last30=Hong |first30=J. T. |display-authors=29 }}</ref> 但中微子的质量大小并没有被测定。这是因为中微子振荡只与不同质量本征态的质量的平方差有关。<ref>{{cite journal |arxiv=hep-ph/0510213 |bibcode=2007RPPh...70.1757M |doi=10.1088/0034-4885/70/11/R02 |title=Theory of neutrinos: A white paper |journal=Reports on Progress in Physics |volume=70 |issue=11 |pages=1757 |year=2007 |last1=Mohapatra |first1=R N |last2=Antusch |first2=S |last3=Babu |first3=K S |last4=Barenboim |first4=G |last5=Chen |first5=M-C |last6=De Gouvêa |first6=A |last7=De Holanda |first7=P |last8=Dutta |first8=B |last9=Grossman |first9=Y |last10=Joshipura |first10=A |last11=Kayser |first11=B |last12=Kersten |first12=J |last13=Keum |first13=Y Y |last14=King |first14=S F |last15=Langacker |first15=P |last16=Lindner |first16=M |last17=Loinaz |first17=W |last18=Masina |first18=I |last19=Mocioiu |first19=I |last20=Mohanty |first20=S |last21=Murayama |first21=H |last22=Pa